$(function(){$(".change-sleep").on("click",function(e){var a=$(this).data("id"),t=$(this).data("newsleep"),n={sleepy:t};$.ajax("/api/cats/"+a,{type:"PUT",data:n}).then(function(){console.log("changed sleep to",t),location.reload()})}),$(".create-form").on("submit",function(e){e.preventDefault();e={name:$("#ca").val().trim(),sleepy:$("[name=sleepy]:checked").val().trim()};$.ajax("/api/cats",{type:"POST",data:e}).then(function(){console.log("created new cat"),location.reload()})})});